{"type": "article", "id": 30544, "title": "被羊毛织物包裹的家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-03T23:04:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160803215745d6ZV3LsgEqHvOykQ.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>到了冬天，你和你的家具或许都需要一件厚厚的外套：Studio Hopkins 推出的 Parka 系列就将羊毛织物与白蜡木结合在一起，营造出了独特的北欧风格。这种罕见的材质组合减轻了木制家具带给人们的那种坚硬感，透露着一股居家气息，简洁的造型适用于各种不同的装修风格。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.studiohopkins.com/parka-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，价格从 750 到 2950 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803222133hefTmIaZpz9k5O70.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803222133jSHygmrzPRbwXMs8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803222133XzE9pbY7vwuCtNei.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608032221347MTkYnG21fVRxur5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}